<title><![CDATA[Fresh Grape Chutney with Ginger and Black Onion Seeds]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[This is a really fresh and unusual chutney that pairs well with a creamy chicken curry. I also like it with sweet potato cakes fried in a bit of butter.

Makes around 2 cups of chutney that will keep in the fridge for a few days.]]></description>
