<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">
<step><![CDATA[Toast the black onion seeds in a dry frying pan over medium heat for 3-5 minutes until they begin to pop. Grind the seeds in a mortar and pestle.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Mix the ground seeds with the remaining ingredients and toss well to combine. Add sea salt and pepper to taste. Allow to sit for at least 30 minutes before serving to allow the flavours to develop.]]></step>
</directions>
